### 3.4 Multi-Field Validation Errors (DRF)

**❌ BAD**
```json
{
  "email": ["This field is required."],
  "password": ["This field may not be blank."]
}
```

**✅ GOOD**
```json
{
  "success": false,
  "errors": [
    {
      "code": "VALIDATION__MISSING_FIELD",
      "details": { "field": "email", "location": "body" }
    },
    {
      "code": "VALIDATION__MISSING_FIELD",
      "details": { "field": "password", "location": "body" }
    }
  ],
  "meta": { "request_id": "req_01HX7Z...", "version": "v1" }
}
```

