### 3.6 Rate Limiting

**❌ BAD**
```python
return Response({"message": "Too many requests. Try again later."}, status=429)
```

**✅ GOOD**
```python
return Response(
    {
        "success": False,
        "error": {
            "code": "RATE_LIMIT__EXCEEDED",
            "details": {
                "limit": 100,
                "window_seconds": 3600,
                "retry_after_seconds": 42,
                "reset_at": "2024-10-01T12:00:00Z"
            }
        },
        "meta": {"request_id": request.id, "version": "v1"},
    },
    status=429,
)
```

